{
  "stem": "23942.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Until today, if you come that-- to the village and you ask some neighbors, they will call my grandmother not by her name, but they remember her by-- call her [NON-ENGLISH], which means the one who-- who ground the, the, the, the-- I guess the kasha or whatever.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And you know, she was a very hardworking woman, my grandmother, with her husband.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They worked side by side.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And on the side, in the same house, they had their own house, a larger house than we lived in.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They had their own house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It sat on a big piece of ground.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And-- and it had also a little store in the same house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So there was, like, a little store that had all sorts of notions and even maybe some sugar and flour that immediately, if you wanted to buy something, you know, that-- because they weren't too many-- very few stores in that area.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "This was in the-- away from the main what you call the shtetl, where the Jewish people lived, where there were some stores.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "This was-- in this area, they were not stores.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So my grandmother had some things like needles and threads and all kinds of-- and candy.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That was the one that I liked the best.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I used to go into the-- and there was a whole shelf of jars with candy.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And my grandmother, that was-- those are my most wonderful memories between me and my grandmother, when she would take me, open up the store.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she would say, which candy do you want?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I-- she would go to one of the jars and it's like saying, eeny, meeny, miny, moe, which one?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was hard to decide because I was a big nosher.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
